::Magmatron/Bobertron/Pantron::

    "Shredder, I have finally picked up your signal, ahh, and you have a 
visitor. What faction is he?" Magmatron said to the comm.
    Bobertron and Pantron came into the room. They both looked very angry. 
Magmatron started to pry Bobertron's mind for what it was. The Key to the 
Ark. Megatron has it, this is very bad indeed.
    "Bobertron, I already know what you want to do, and don't try it, I can 
make you stop if I wish," Magmatron said to Bobertron. "Instead, go and be 
back up for Shredder, here are his coordinates."
